transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hi, thank you for calling Viagra.

Speaker 2: How can I assist you?

Speaker 1: Yeah, I received an order of pills that I had not ordered.

Speaker 2: The last time I talked, they was not going to send me any more until I called them.

Speaker 1: Then they went ahead and sent another order.

Speaker 2: OK, what's your name and your date of birth?

Speaker 1: My name is David Beach.

Speaker 2: Date of birth is 10-11-1963.

Speaker 1: What's your ZIP code?

Speaker 2: 64682.

Speaker 1: You say your name is David?

Speaker 2: Correct.

Speaker 1: And your last name is D-E-I-T-C-H?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: OK, yes, I do see here that you are a VAP with us, so you do have a prescription active with us for Cialis 20 milligrams, which you do receive every four months.

Speaker 2: Is it that you have enough supply right now?

Speaker 1: What's going on?

Speaker 2: I do.

Speaker 1: I've got plenty for right now.

Speaker 2: That's why it was put on hold.

Speaker 1: Yeah, no worries.

Speaker 2: So what I can go ahead and do for you right now is that I can go ahead and just extend that hold, and I can pause it for another six months, OK?

Speaker 1: OK, that works.

Speaker 2: OK, you're all set.

Speaker 1: If you need any supply before that time, feel free to give us a call, OK?

Speaker 2: OK, all righty, thank you.

Speaker 1: You're welcome.

Speaker 2: Have a nice day.

Speaker 1: Bye.
